 pr√©f√©rer votre codes aux d√©pendances tiers.</p><h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="optimiser-les-images">Optimiser les images<a href="app-size#optimiser-les-images" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Optimiser les images" title="Direct link to Optimiser les images">‚Äã</a></h3><p>Selon <a href="https://httparchive.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">l&#x27;archive Http</a>, les images sont les <a href="https://httparchive.org/reports/page-weight#bytesImg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">plus grande contributrice au poids du site</a>. Donc, si votre application inclut des images ou des ic√¥nes, assurez-vous de les optimiser !</p><p>Vous pouvez choisir entre plusieurs options manuelles (<a href="https://www.gimp.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GIMP</a>, <a href="https://www.adobe.com/de/products/photoshop.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Photoshop</a>, <a href="https://squoosh.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Squoosh</a>) ou plugins pour vos outils de construction frontend favoris (<a href="https://github.com/JonasKruckenberg/imagetools" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">vite-imagetools</a>, <a href="https://github.com/vbenjs/vite-plugin-imagemin" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">vite-plugin-imagemin</a>, <a href="https://github.com/webpack-contrib/image-minimizer-webpack-plugin" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">image-minimizer-webpack-plugin</a>).</p><p>Notez que la biblioth√®que <code>imagemin</code> est le plugin le plus utilis√© mais il est <a href="https://github.com/imagemin/imagemin/issues/385" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">officiellement plus maintenue</a>.</p><h4 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="utiliser-les-formats-dimage-modernes">Utiliser les formats d&#x27;image modernes<a href="app-size#utiliser-les-formats-dimage-modernes" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Utiliser les formats d&#x27;image modernes"